{"id":2186,"title":"04 | 企业应该在什么时候开始考虑引入微服务？","content":"<h1>温馨提示</h1>\n<p>部分Android用户如果在全屏播放时遇到问题，建议使用 PC 版或微信小程序进行学习。给您造成的不便还请谅解，我们会尽快解决这一问题。</p>\n<p>PC端学习方式</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>用浏览器访问 <a href=\"https://time.geekbang.org\">https://time.geekbang.org</a> ，登录极客时间账号</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>访问 <a href=\"https://time.geekbang.org/paid-content\">https://time.geekbang.org/paid-content</a> ，选择相应内容</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>小程序学习方式</p>\n<ul>\n<li>进入极客时间小程序</li>\n<li>在视频课程里选择相应内容</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- special end -->\n","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":2373,"user_name":"LMD","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1013443,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7626FBB7A4E771","user_header":"","comment_is_top":true,"comment_ctime":1516964761,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"关于《微服务架构核心20讲》课程讲义（PDF 文件），学员可复制下面链接到浏览器下载获取。 http:&#47;&#47;t.cn&#47;RQs9iTw","like_count":15},{"had_liked":false,"id":9250,"user_name":"颇忒妥","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1026448,"ip_address":"","ucode":"AA86AD1049BC2E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/a9/90/0c5ed3d9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1526704627,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":2781,"content":"对，如果团队没有能力搞定单块应用，没有基本的模块化，分层分治思维，那么也别指望微服务能成为救星","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1526736154,"ip_address":"","comment_id":9250,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"单块优先逐步微服务的前提是单块本身的架构设计良好，比如按模块、按类库开发业务功能，保证业务代码之间的松耦合，可以考虑采用DDD来指导设计。如果原来的代码一团乱麻，那微服务也救不了你。","like_count":10,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":418008,"discus